{
  "id": "L1",
  "title": "First Day at Language School",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Benvenuto! Welcome to your first Italian lesson. We'll learn just what you need to introduce yourself to a new classmate."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L1_E01",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Ciao",
        "meaning": "Hello / Hi"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L1_P01",
      "data": {
        "word": "Ciao",
        "phonetic": "[ˈtʃaːo]",
        "tip": "The 'ci' sound in Italian is like the 'ch' in 'cheese'."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L1_E02",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Mi chiamo...",
        "meaning": "My name is..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L1_P02",
      "data": {
        "word": "chiamo",
        "phonetic": "[ˈkjaːmo]",
        "tip": "The 'chi' combination sounds like a hard 'k' in English, as in 'key'."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L1_E03",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Come ti chiami?",
        "meaning": "What's your name?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L1_E04",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Piacere",
        "meaning": "Nice to meet you"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L1_S01",
      "title": "Initial Introductions",
      "setting": "You are in your Italian class before the lesson starts. A classmate turns to you and says hello.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Ciao!"
        },
        {
          "title": "Respond to the greeting and state your name",
          "extract_info": {
            "user_name": "Extract the user's name from their message"
          }
        },
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Piacere, {user_name}!"
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask for their name"
        },
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Mi chiamo Luca."
        },
        {
          "title": "State that it's nice to meet them"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Great start! Now let's learn how to ask and say where you are from. A simple 'E tu?' is a great way to ask 'And you?'."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L1_E05",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Di dove sei?",
        "meaning": "Where are you from?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L1_E06",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Sono di...",
        "meaning": "I am from..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L1_V01",
      "data": {
        "l'Inghilterra": "England"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L1_V02",
      "data": {
        "gli Stati Uniti": "the United States"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L1_P03",
      "data": {
        "word": "gli",
        "phonetic": "[ʎi]",
        "tip": "This is a unique Italian sound, similar to the 'lli' in the English word 'million'."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L1_E07",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "E tu?",
        "meaning": "And you?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L1_E08",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Abito a...",
        "meaning": "I live in..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L1_S02",
      "title": "Exchanging Origins",
      "setting": "The conversation continues with your new classmate, Luca.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Piacere mio."
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask Luca where he is from"
        },
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Sono di Roma. E tu?"
        },
        {
          "title": "State your country of origin",
          "extract_info": {
            "user_country": "Extract the user's country from their message"
          }
        },
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Ah, {user_country}! Bello. Io abito qui a Milano."
        },
        {
          "title": "Mention the city you currently live in",
          "extract_info": {
            "user_city": "Extract the user's city from their message"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "'A dopo' is a friendly, informal way to say goodbye when you expect to see the person again very soon."
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L1_V03",
      "data": {
        "La lezione": "The lesson"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L1_E09",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Oh",
        "meaning": "Oh"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L1_E10",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Inizia la lezione",
        "meaning": "The lesson is starting"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L1_E11",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Buona fortuna",
        "meaning": "Good luck"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L1_E12",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Grazie",
        "meaning": "Thank you"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L1_E13",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Anche a te",
        "meaning": "You too"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L1_E14",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "A dopo",
        "meaning": "See you later"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L1_S03",
      "title": "Wrapping up the First Chat",
      "setting": "The teacher has just walked in and is about to start the class.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Ah, {user_city}. Bene."
        },
        {
          "title": "Acknowledge that the lesson is starting"
        },
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Sì, è vero."
        },
        {
          "title": "Wish them good luck"
        },
        {
          "chatbot_message": "Grazie! Anche a te."
        },
        {
          "title": "Say goodbye for now"
        },
        {
          "chatbot_message": "A dopo!"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}